      <div1 id="BQ-42-2-0009">
        <div2>
          <head>
            <title type="main">Response to Helen P. Bruder</title>
          </head>
          <byline>By <docAuthor>Anne K. <name>Mellor</name></docAuthor></byline>
          <p>I HAVE my opinion of the value of Bruder’s collection, already expressed, and she has hers. I
don’t disagree with anything she says; I just didn’t find her method of organization—or goals for the
volume—helpful. Readers of course should consult the volume itself and make up their own minds.</p>
        </div2>
      </div1>
